text: Prime Commercial Land in Pauls Valley!

Prime 1.83-acre commercial lot with C-5 zoning and high visibility along I-35. Located on the service road between Starbucks and McDonald's, near established businesses including restaurants, a truck stop, and auto dealerships.
Seller has approved plans for a restaurant building. One of the few remaining sites available in this area.
